high_descs: Turn right and move towards the door on the right and then turn left and move toward and face the microwave.
Open the microwave door and pick up the mug to the left of the glass and then close the microwave door.
Turn around, move forward, turn right and move toward the door then turn right and face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door and place the mug on the shelf to the left of the bowl. Close the refrigerator door, wait, and open the refrigerator door pick up the mug next to the bowl and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and move towards the oven and then turn right and face the coffee maker.
Place the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug on a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the opposite wall. Turn left at the wall and go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, take out the white coffee mug and close the microwave door.
Turn to your left and go forward until you come to the fridge. Turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the mug into the fridge, then take it back out and close the fridge.
Turn around to your left and walk to the sink, then turn right to face the coffee maker to the right of the sink.
Place the mug under the spout of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Take a mug from the microwave to the coffeemaker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave in the corner on the opposite side of the room
Open the microwave and remove the white mug from it
Turn left and walk over to the fridge
Put the mug into the fridge then remove it
Turn left and walk around to the coffee machine on the kitchen counter
Put the mug down on the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: Put the white mug on the coffee machine
